{"_path":"/councilor/service/s4069","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"文德公園人行道增闢","description":null,"image":"/images/service/4069-1.jpeg","sequence":4069,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.4 強化區域交通規劃","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1EoJ5864gB/","author":"陳雅倫","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"陳雅倫"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-11-20T00:00:00.000Z","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"文德公園人行道增闢"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"文德公園人行道增闢"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1EoJ5864gB/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"陳雅倫"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 2024/11/20:"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"雅倫從今年五月就開始協調的文德公園人行通道，目前規劃在 #樂學路 #長慶三街口 行穿線處【新設樓梯及無障礙斜坡道】至文德公園！讓通行安全又便利～"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 進出零阻礙：無障礙斜坡道，讓輪椅、嬰兒車使用者輕鬆到公園！"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n✅ 貼心規劃：樓梯設置方便行人快速通行！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4069-1.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4069-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"11 月份方案出爐，再度現場討論，希望市府儘速撥給預算，讓通道趕快完成"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s4069-2.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s4069-2.jpeg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前現況如上圖，此處是 A7 重劃區-樂善國小生活圈通往文德公園及文德舊社區的主要人行通道，目前的泥巴路由雅倫議員爭取改建為階梯＋無障礙斜坡道。 "},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"代表附近居民感謝雅倫"}]},{"type":"tex